  "prompt": "Which is the best suitable bike (budget: 70-80k), for a guy who is 5'5\" and 52kg in a city with high traffic for a daily commute in India?",
  "response": "For a daily commute in a city with high traffic in India, it's important to consider a bike that is comfortable, fuel-efficient, and easy to maneuver. Given your budget of 70,000 to 80,000 INR, here are a few options that might suit your needs:\n\n1. **Honda SP 125**\n   - **Engine**: 124cc\n   - **Mileage**: Around 65-70 km/l\n   - **Features**: Digital instrument cluster, LED headlamp, Honda Eco Technology for better fuel efficiency.\n   - **Suitable For**: Comfortable ride, reliable, and good fuel efficiency.\n\n2. **TVS Radeon**\n   - **Engine**: 109.7cc\n   - **Mileage**: Around 65-70 km/l\n   - **Features**: ComforTec technology, LED DRL, and Dual-tone seat.\n   - **Suitable For**: Comfortable seating and a robust build, slightly lower seat height which might be ideal for your height.\n\n3. **Hero Glamour**\n   - **Engine**: 124.7cc\n   - **Mileage**: Around 60-65 km/l\n   - **Features**: Xsens technology, robust design, digital-analog console.\n   - **Suitable For**: Good mix of style and performance, with a comfortable ride.\n\n4. **Bajaj Pulsar 125 Neon**\n   - **Engine**: 124.4cc\n   - **Mileage**: Around 50-55 km/l\n   - **Features**: Neon highlights, iconic Pulsar design.\n   - **Suitable For**: Sportier looks and performance, if you're looking for a more powerful option.\n\n5. **Hero Super Splendor**\n   - **Engine**: 124.7cc\n   - **Mileage**: Around 60-70 km/l\n   - **Features**: Xsens with FI technology, Integrated Braking System.\n   - **Suitable For**: Comfortable for city commuting, offers a great balance of power and efficiency.\n\nThese bikes are known for their reliability and should serve well for daily commuting, especially in high traffic. Since you're 5'5\", be sure to do a test ride to ensure comfort, particularly regarding seat height and overall ergonomics. Additionally, consider checking the latest on-road prices and any ongoing offers at local dealerships to ensure the best deal within your budget.",
